verse = \lyricmode {
  They speak with scorn and haugh -- ti -- ness;
they scoff, and threa -- ten to op -- press.
Their mouth lays claim to heav -- en's re -- gions;
their tongue de -- mands the earth's al -- le -- giance.
So peo -- ple turn to praise these men,
and they can find no fault with them.
\"God does not see it,\" they de -- clare.
The Most High does not know or care.
}
